    "description": "<strong>Manage your restaurant</strong><br><br>During the first 9 days of Don Duality, you'll have the chance to enhance and expand your restaurant. Purchase extra tables to seat more customers and advertise to increase your popularity and draw in a larger crowd. However, be aware that as your restaurant becomes more successful, you'll need to hire additional staff to keep up with the demand.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388170/extras/9fef9485620749af2ee48d00ed234a91.poster.avif?t=1692636027\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388170/extras/9fef9485620749af2ee48d00ed234a91.webm?t=1692636027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Lead a Mafia organization</strong><br><br>Take control of your criminal empire in Don Duality by commanding your gangster subordinates to engage in a range of activities, including robbing banks, collecting debts, and intimidating law enforcement. Choose your missions carefully to maximize profits and establish your dominance in the underworld.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388170/extras/72ad8fd401202ca9e631acdc0b643b91.poster.avif?t=1692636027\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388170/extras/72ad8fd401202ca9e631acdc0b643b91.webm?t=1692636027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Watch for random events</strong><br><br>Beware of marked cards with a bell. Each time you receive one, it adds to the bell's progress bar. When it's full, a significant event is triggered that can seriously impact your business<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388170/extras/22e88c26fc890e7aebc725ae2b02d621.poster.avif?t=1692636027\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388170/extras/22e88c26fc890e7aebc725ae2b02d621.webm?t=1692636027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Launder your money </strong><br><br>Consider money laundering daily. Wealth attracts police attention. Maxed out concern leads to arrest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388170/extras/0374cf3bf077cdba30f7eca48dbb78f8.poster.avif?t=1692636027\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388170/extras/0374cf3bf077cdba30f7eca48dbb78f8.webm?t=1692636027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
